ero idle cost, no EC2 needed)\n   594\t\n   595\t---\n   596\t\n   597\t## Monit
oring\n   598\t\n   599\t### CloudWatch Metric Filter — Pipeline Failures\n   60
0\t\n   601\t```bash\n   602\taws logs put-metric-filter \\\n   603\t  --log-gro
