2\t  --alarm-actions arn:aws:sns:us-east-1:ACCOUNT:tokenfly-alerts\n   623\t```\
n   624\t\n   625\t### Key metrics to watch\n   626\t| Metric | Threshold | Acti
on |\n   627\t|--------|-----------|--------|\n   628\t| Pipeline FAILED in logs
